supports the
			 designation of January 28, 2014, as National Data Privacy
			 Day;

encourages State
			 and local governments to observe the day with appropriate activities and
			 initiatives that raise awareness about data privacy and security;

encourages
			 corporations, governments, and other relevant organizations to take steps to protect the privacy and security of individuals and to promote trust in
			 technologies;
